<P><PB N="3" REF="8">The Government allowing the Company 20 Years Purcha&s;e for every long Annuity, and 14 Years Purcha&s;e for every &s;hort One, gives them a Liberty to create 30,981,698<HI>l.</HI> or thereabouts, new Stock, and thereby to enlarge their Capital till it amounts to 42,184,408<HI>l.</HI> Stock or thereabouts. Thus much for the particular Branches to be taken into the Stock.</P>
<P>Secondly, Let us enquire into the Amount of the <HI>South-Sea</HI> Stock, provided the whole Debt was &s;ub&s;cribed upon the Terms pro|po&s;ed: And upon this Head, it will be nece&s;&s;ary to di&s;tingui&s;h, between that Part of the irredeemable Debt &s;ub&s;cribed la&s;t <HI>April</HI> at 375<HI>l.</HI> and the remaining Part thereof, together with the redeemable Debt to be taken in at 400<HI>l. per Cent.</HI></P>
