<P><PB N="4" REF="9">It is to be ob&s;erved, that the la&s;t men|tioned Capital may not be perfectly exact, by rea&s;on no Di&s;tinction is made between the 99 Years Annuities, and the 14 <HI>per Cents,</HI> they both being included under one Head of Long Annuities, and the like Years Purcha&s;e in Stock given for each. The &s;ame is to be ob&s;erved of the Lottery 1710, where Blanks and Prizes are likewi&s;e inclu|ded under the &s;ame Head: But this cau&s;es little Difference in the Capital Stock given for either, but only in the Bonds.</P>
