<P><PB N="5" REF="10">Hence it is evident, that about 10,325,824<HI>l.</HI> Capital Stock, or thereabouts, would re|deem the whole 30,981,706<HI>l.</HI> of Debts, &s;uppo&s;ing the &s;ame to be all &s;ub&s;cribed into the Stock upon the before-mentioned Terms: The Bonds excepted in this Account.<TABLE>
